This directory contains material for Staff Report 328

    V.V. Chari, Patrick Kehoe, and Ellen McGrattan 
    Business Cycle Accounting
    Econometrica, forthcoming

Directory      DESCRIPTION
----------     ----------------------------------------------------
depression     Codes for computing decision functions (Great Depression)   
mleannual      Codes and annual data for maximum likelihood estimation 
mleqtrly       Codes and quarterly data for maximum likelihood estimation 
results        Figures in the main text and appendices
tex            TeX files for paper, slides, appendices

Ellen McGrattan
